rse is dedicated to the analysis of texts and concepts; students will make brief oral presentations; regularly submit written responses; and write a final, sustained research essay."}, {"name": "Class Materials (Required)", "value": "Aby Warburg, The Renewal of Pagan Antiquity, 1999, 9780892365371; G. Didi-Huberman, The Surviving Image, 9780271072081; article-length readings will be made available on CANVAS"}], "lmod": "2/8/17 6:40 PM (CT)", "subject": "ART_HIST"}]
